{"tid":2202850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「鐵證」178萬人檢測係一個騙局","createTime":"2020-09-15T02:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T04:09:42.000Z","uid":99805,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c3fb63a9c354d3c55252c9414d115d627f5acda","tid":2202850,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:32:13.000Z","msg":"政府意圖用人（次）好大喜功<br />\n178萬人（數）同178萬人（次）<br />\n係兩樣好大分別既數據<br />\n<br />\n人次，一般用作使用率統計<br />\n例如地鐵今日有100萬人次搭<br />\n咁樣係包括一個人可以上上落落搭十次八次<br />\n只係反映有幾多人試用地鐵<br />\n<br />\n人數，先係反映實際社會情況有幾多人參與<br />\n有100萬不同既人投票<br />\n咁係反映社會民意<br />\n但係1個人投100萬次<br />\n呢個就係假意見，小學生都識既道理<br />\n<br />\n而事實上now搵到一個受訪暫驗完又驗<br />\n所以呢178萬根本無科學參考價值<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgJ0N7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgJ0N7d.png&h=bd3de275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPP7s7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPP7s7g.png&h=85d160ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZ65ZdW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZ65ZdW.png&h=6df1f8ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">退後一百萬步講，做數先做得178萬你都好意思拎出黎打飛機？柒婆，乜你以前23分就夠拎第一啦？</span></span>"},{"pid":"993fb34f91fe17bc591bf73f0c968aa7d8f41180","tid":2202850,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:32:30.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"a726af88a3c4bb8a0d14f3dc55e8a56973f00eaa","tid":2202850,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"我為什麼要關注妓女?"},{"pid":"70c656b48e57420584b38392ab82ddefa6c05e1b","tid":2202850,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:35:54.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"4be2f70e5441aa3a2834ff29db944ef47805a5e4","tid":2202850,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15